window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Multiaward-winning statisticians, directors and cofounders of the Gapminder Foundation Ola and Anna Rosling talk to Audible about the release of <i>Factfulness: Ten Reasons We’re Wrong about the World - and Why Things Are Better than You Think</i>. </p> <p>Continuing on with the work of legendary scientist and public educator Hans Rosling, the two introduce their revolutionary audiobook and begin to explain the many reasons behind the widespread ignorance of the global population. They also provide useful tips and resources which will encourage the pursuit of facts and statistics. Listeners will gain unique insight into the minds of two of Sweden’s most influential scholars of our time.</p>"; 
